latestIgtvVideos.title: HOW TO ACHIEVE FLAWLESS BASE?
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Getting a flawless base is really important for each one to get a skin like finish. 
Here are some ways and tricks to achieve a FLAWLESS BASE
1. Make sure you cleanse your skin properly before applying anything on your skin
-The key to truly great makeup is in the 
2. SKIN PREP:
••Toner: @richfeeltrichology|Lip balm: @khadinatural ••Moisturiser will help you to achieve smooth base
(Pro tip: Take a few minute extra and make sure you massage the moisturiser efficienctly into your skin) MOISTURISER: @clinique_in •• Primer will smooth out the skin’s texture, minimise pores and give your foundation the perfect surface to cling on (Pro tip: Dont massage primer on face make sure you pat the primer gently on your face) PRIMER: @lorealparis -After prepping up your skin next,
•• Colour Corrector- @kaybykatrina 
Use Peach corrector if you have minimal pigmentations and orange corrector if you have more.
If you need that extra glowy and dewy skin like finish use
•• Essential Rose Gold Oil: @indulgeo.essentials •• Foundation: @hudabeauty in the shade butter pecan (ProTip: Once your done with brush application of foundation, Use a damp sponge and blend everything together.
Dont forget your neck)
•• Concealer- @maybelline Age rewind in the shade medium
BLEND BLEND BLEND, BLEND EVERYTHNG - Last but not the least, you’ll want to fix all your work firmly in place. Set your face
(ProTip: Don’t ever forget to set your face because that will lock down all those layers, remove any excess shine and ensure that everything stays looking fresh for longer)
Loose Powder: @maybelline in the shade Light Medium
(ProTip: Use that previous damp sponge that you used for foundation to set your face, it will give you skin like finish
Then, once your whole makeup is finished, grab a makeup setting spray and spritz all over your skin. It will fix everything firmly in place
There you go with FLAWLESS BASE😍❤️
.
.
Do let me know in the comments if this was helpful
@makeme_up__
